{"tid":271471,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先公司有個醜女俾佢男神串到一棟都冇","createTime":"2017-06-05T06:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T11:23:00.000Z","uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39db033b40328c3f2c13e791f674b30ec72cd81a","tid":271471,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:10:35.000Z","msg":"醜女：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    佢男神：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢男神同啲男同事傾去邊區141叫雞好<br />\n<br />\n個醜女係邊邊扮斟水飲<br />\n<br />\n個醜女見佢地傾完計之後 突登走埋佢男神度講<br />\n<br />\n醜女：呀⋯⋯Dunson ,估唔到你有叫雞,好Dirty 囉 真係對你好失望 扣晒分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢男神：哦 係咩 ？扣幾分呀？扣完又點？慢慢扣飽佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 污唔污糟又點？我又唔會同你做，影唔影響你呀？你咁中意理人既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見住個醜女眼泛淚光咁妹下妹下走返自己位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff1a8df481e3d20a62da4c9bff6c530a2b5af24","tid":271471,"uid":21423,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:15:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cfb886761f3b8a1272e1f63d642e38b0fe1f218","tid":271471,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>然後個醜女就喊住咁開咗呢個post</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66461a40a2a8dd7b86755796f4ad9ae297362a1","tid":271471,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:38:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>然後個醜女就喊住咁開咗呢個post</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbc1744a9764b2be80135f7fb536da48936c13c","tid":271471,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>然後個醜女就喊住咁開咗呢個post</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm